OL,3,CWhy has Birmingham's Ozzy the Bull got
OL,4,Ca Peaky Blinders makeover?
OL,6,FCommuters at Birmingham's New Street
OL,7,FStation might have mistaken Ozzy the
OL,8,FBull for Tommy Shelby from Peaky
OL,9,FBlinders.
OL,11,FThe 33ft-high mechanical bull has been
OL,12,Fgiven a makeover (a flat cap to be
OL,13,Fexact) and has a red carpet laid out
OL,14,Fat its feet - to mark the launch of
OL,15,Fthe new film Peaky Blinders: The
OL,16,FImmortal Man.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
