OL,3,CWhy has Birmingham's Ozzy the Bull got
OL,4,Ca Peaky Blinders makeover?
OL,6,FIn partnership with Visit Birmingham
OL,7,Fand the West Midlands, and Network
OL,8,FRail, the station concourse is playing
OL,9,Fhost to period-inspired scenic
OL,10,Felements reflecting early 20th-century
OL,11,FBirmingham.
OL,13,FFree portraits are being offered to
OL,14,Fmembers of the public between 12pm and
OL,15,F6pm from Friday until Monday, March 2,
OL,16,Fahead of the premiere of the film,
OL,17,Fwhich is set in Birmingham during the
OL,18,FFirst World War.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
