OL,3,CWhy has Birmingham's Ozzy the Bull got
OL,4,Ca Peaky Blinders makeover?
OL,6,FThe staffed photo facility will offer
OL,7,Fprinted keepsake portraits, allowing
OL,8,Fthousands of fans to celebrate
OL,9,FBirmingham's film heritage.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the station, Martin Simms,
OL,12,Fhead of film and TV support agency
OL,13,FProduction Central WM, said: "New
OL,14,FStreet Station is one of the most
OL,15,Fvisited stations outside of London and
OL,16,FI think the fact that this is such a
OL,17,Fglobal phenomenon ` Peaky Blinders
OL,18,Fitself ` it only feels right that it's
OL,19,Fin the heart of Birmingham, which is
OL,20,Fwhere the original story has come
OL,21,Ffrom."
OL,26,@uD@^OU}D@FO]
