OL,3,CWhy has Birmingham's Ozzy the Bull got
OL,4,Ca Peaky Blinders makeover?
OL,6,FAsked about the impact of the hit
OL,7,Fseries on local screen tourism, Mr
OL,8,FSimms added: "There's been an increase
OL,9,Fof 50% (in) US visitors coming to
OL,10,FBirmingham as a result of Peaky
OL,11,FBlinders.
OL,13,F"It's got that wide reach, which
OL,14,Freally puts us on the map to really be
OL,15,Fable to let people know more of what's
OL,16,Fhere in general, and increase the
OL,17,Feconomy."
OL,26,@pD@NOUuD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
