OL,3,CWhy has Birmingham's Ozzy the Bull got
OL,4,Ca Peaky Blinders makeover?
OL,6,FFilming of Peaky Blinders: The
OL,7,FImmortal Man alone had pumped around
OL,8,F#1 million into the local economy, he
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,FAsked if he could reveal any specific
OL,12,Fnearby locations used to shoot the
OL,13,Ffilm, Mr Simms said: "I won't spoil it
OL,14,Ffor everyone but there are some very
OL,15,Fwell-known locations ` some connected
OL,16,Fwith areas around the Council House
OL,17,Fand such, and then also Digbeth Loc.
OL,18,FStudios, which is also at the heart of
OL,19,Fthings."
OL,26,@uD@VOU{D@HO]
