OL,3,CWhy has Birmingham's Ozzy the Bull got
OL,4,Ca Peaky Blinders makeover?
OL,6,FProduction Central WM is the region's
OL,7,Fdedicated production services agency
OL,8,Fand is backed by the West Midlands
OL,9,FCombined Authority, bringing together
OL,10,Flocations, crew and facilities for
OL,11,Fcontent producers.
OL,13,FOzzy, named in honour of late rock
OL,14,Flegend Ozzy Osbourne, was installed at
OL,15,Fthe station in 2023, a year after the
OL,16,Fmoving sculpture formed the much-loved
OL,17,Fcentrepiece of the Commonwealth Games
OL,18,Fopening ceremony.
